high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the television
Pick up the keys on the right side of the television
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward, turn left in front of the coffee table
Put the keys on the coffee table
Turn left, go forward, turn right in front of the television, go forward a bit, turn right
Pick up the keys on the left side of the television
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward, turn left in front of the coffee table
Put the keys on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Bring two sets of keys to the coffee table

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the bed then turn right and go to the dresser with the TV on it.
Take the keys from the right side of the dresser.
Turn around and turn left then walk around the green chair to the round table on the right side of the chair.
Put the keys on the table.
Turn left and walk past the green chair then turn right at and walk to the the dresser with the TV on it.
Pick up the keys from the left side of the dresser.
Turn left and walk past the green chair then turn left to the small round table.
Put the keys on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and then veer right to the TV stand.
Pick up the keys on the right side of the TV stand.
Turn right and walk to the small round table in the corner on the left.
Place the keys on the table between the mug and the remote control.
Turn left and walk back to the TV stand, this time to the far side of it.
Pick up the keys on the TV stand.
Walk around the TV stand and straight ahead, back to the table in the corner.
Place the keys on the corner table, to the left of the blue pen.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on a table.
